  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger and saute until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the curry powder, thyme, and scotch bonnet pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lentils, coconut milk, and vegetable broth, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes or until the lentils are tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with roti."
